Wendy’s Says It Is Moving Company Headquarters to Ohio

-- B y   L e s l i e   P a t t o n   a n d   M a r k   N i q u e t t e
-- 
2011-08-04T14:26:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-04/wendy-s-says-it-is-moving-company-headquarters-to-ohio.html
Wendy’s Co., the operator of the
Wendy’s fast-food chain, said it will move company headquarters
to Dublin,  Ohio .  “Today we are making official: Wendy’s is moving its
corporate headquarters back to Ohio,” Roland Smith, president
and chief executive officer of Wendy’s, said at a press
conference at the company’s offices in Dublin, Ohio. The company
will make a “multimillion dollar” renovation to its Dublin
campus, he said.  Previously the company was based in Atlanta.  To contact the reporters on this story: Leslie Patton in Chicago
at   lpatton5@bloomberg.net ; Mark Niquette in
Columbus at   mniquette@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Robin Ajello at   rajello@bloomberg.net  